                </li>
                <li>
                    Add a new breeding record.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-section">
            <h4><a href="">Manage Birth Records</a></h4>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    View birth records and statistics.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Add a new birth.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-section">
            <h4><a href="">Generate Reports</a></h4>
